msgid ""
"Establish the need for free software development experience as a condition "
"of technical solvency."
msgstr ""
"Establir la necessitat d’experiència en codi obert com a condició de "
"solvència tècnica."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:175
msgid ""
"However many conditions are included in the contract, if the winning company "
"has no experience of participating in free software projects, it is most "
"likely that the product and the development process will end up not "
"following many free software development conventions.  In most cases, there "
"is no reason why that should be the result of bad faith but a lack of "
"knowledge."
msgstr ""
"Per moltes condicions que es posin al contracte, si l’empresa adjudicatària "
"no té experiència participant en projectes de codi obert, el més probable és "
"que el producte no acabi sent obert del tot. En la majoria de casos això no "
"té perquè ser resultat d’una mala disposició, sinó fruit del desconeixement."

#. type: Block title
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:178
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Enter into a subsidiary independent validation and verification (IV&V) "
"contract"
msgstr ""
"Fer un contracte secundari de validació i verificació independent (IV&V)"

#.   links incoming: link:#M_F60[_M_F60_]
#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:190
msgid ""
"Hire a company that does have proven experience of sustained participation "
"in free software projects.  This company will act as an external project "
"collaborator and carry out code checks and process analyses, reporting "
"directly to IMI."
msgstr ""
"Contractar alguna entitat que sí tingui experiència demostrable en "
"participar de manera sostinguda en projectes de codi obert. Aquesta entitat "
"actuarà com un col·laborador extern del projecte i farà revisions de codi i "
"anàlisis de processos, reportant directament a l’IMI."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:192
msgid ""
"In an free software project, what is being contracted is not just the code "
"but also the process."
msgstr ""
"En un projecte de codi obert el que s’està contractant no és només el codi, "
"sinó també el procés."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:194
msgid "Add this service to the project technical office."
msgstr "Afegir aquest servei a la oficina tècnica del projecte."

#. type: Block title
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:197
#, no-wrap
msgid "Include experience in free software projects as an award criterion"
msgstr ""
"Incloure com a criteri d’adjudicació l’experiència en projectes de codi "
"obert"

#.   links incoming: link:#M_F60[_M_F60_]
#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:208
msgid ""
"Award a set number of points to companies that can certify experience in "
"projects that have produced free software."
msgstr ""
"Adjudicar un determinat nombre de punts a les empreses que acreditin "
"experiència en projectes on s’ha produït programari lliure treballant en "
"obert."

#. type: Block title
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:211
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Ask tenderers to provide evidence of participants' experience in free "
"software projects"
msgstr ""
"Demanar als concursants que acreditin experiència en projectes de codi obert "
"dels participants"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:220
msgid ""
"They must do this by providing references for their individual participation "
"in public repositories and forums (StackOverflow, etc.), from projects they "
"have taken part in."
msgstr ""
"Ho han de fer aportant referències a la seva participació individual en "
"repositoris i fòrums oberts (StackOverflow, etc.), dels projectes en que "
"hagin participat."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:222
msgid ""
"This can be done as a technical solvency criterion or a performance "
"criterion."
msgstr ""
"Es pot fer constar aquesta demanda com a criteri de solvència tècnica o com "
"a criteri d’execució."

#. type: Block title
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:225
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Split the project into groups of features that can be tendered in various "
"lots"
msgstr ""
"Partir el projecte en grups de funcionalitat que es puguin licitar en "
"diferents lots"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:232
msgid ""
"Either by contracting by lots or by outsourcing specific tasks such as "
"checking the code and its deployment, as established by the link:#fer-"
"contracte-validacio-independent[Alternative: Enter into a subsidiary "
"independent validation and verification (IV&V) contract]."
msgstr ""
"Bé sigui contractant per lots, bé sigui externalitzant tasques concretes com "
"la revisió de codi i del desplegament, com estableix la link:#fer-contracte-"
"validacio-independent[Alternativa: Fer un contracte secundari de validació i "
"verificació (IV&V) independent]."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:235
msgid ""
"Besides being a policy in line with the Guide for Technological Procurement, "
"disseminating knowledge of the product is very favourable to the interests "
"of the project.  The _reservoirs of distributed knowledge_ are one of the "
"main strengths of free software projects."
msgstr ""
"A més de ser una política alineada amb la Guia de contractació tecnològica, "
"és molt favorable pels interessos del projecte disseminar el coneixement "
"sobre el producte. Les _reserves de coneixement distribuïdes_ son una de les "
"principals fortaleses dels projectes de codi obert."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:237
msgid ""
"It also helps a great deal to ensure collaborative development processes are "
"established from the outset."
msgstr ""
"També ajuda molt a que des de l’inici del desenvolupament s’estableixin "
"processos de treball en obert."

#. type: Block title
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:240
#, no-wrap
msgid "Reduce the financial stability requirements for tenders"
msgstr "Reduir els requeriments d’estabilitat financera de les ofertes"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:245 modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:290 modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:473
msgid "Integration"
msgstr "Integració"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:251
msgid ""
"This is a matter of softening the required financial solvency criteria.  The "
"aim is avoid putting artificial impediments that prevent small and medium-"
"sized companies and cooperatives from submitting a bid when they meet (often "
"more than large companies) the technical solvency criteria."
msgstr ""
"Es tracta de suavitzar els criteris de solvència financera exigits. "
"L’objectiu és no posar impediments artificials que puguin impedir presentar-"
"se al concurs a empreses i cooperatives petites i mitjanes que compleixin (o "
"fins i tot superin a les grans) en solvència tècnica."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:253
msgid ""
"As explained in the Join Up _Guideline on public procurement of Open Source "
"Software_<document/guideline-public-procurement-open-source-software>, page "
"47, (document commissioned by the European Commission), the greater "
"interoperability and interdependence of suppliers when working with free "
"software increases the sustainability of projects without the need for very "
"high financial requirements."
msgstr ""
"Com s’explica a la joinup:Guideline on public procurement of Open Source "
"Software<document/guideline-public-procurement-open-source-software>, pàgina "
"47, (document encarregat per la Comissió Europea) la major interoperabilitat "
"i independència de proveïdors quan es treballa en codi obert incrementa la "
"sostenibilitat dels projectes sense necessitat d’uns requeriments financers "
"molt elevats."

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:256
#, no-wrap
msgid "Dissemination of the project"
msgstr "Difusió del projecte"

#. type: Block title
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:262
#, no-wrap
msgid "Choose a good name for the project"
msgstr "Escollir un bon nom per al projecte"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:267 modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:279 modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:292 modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:316 modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:337 modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:363 modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:383 modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:397 modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:430 modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:477 modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:500 modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:548 modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:587 modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:644 modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:661 modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:668 modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:687
msgid "Publication"
msgstr "Publicació"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:269
msgid ""
"This is more important in free software projects than in proprietary ones "
"because obtaining the participation of users and developers from outside the "
"confines of the City Council can determine the project’s level of success."
msgstr ""
"Això és més important en projectes de codi obert que en projectes "
"tradicionals perquè adquirir usuaris i desenvolupadors fora dels confins de "
"l’Ajuntament pot determinar el grau d’èxit del projecte."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:271
msgid ""
"More specific pointers can be found at http://producingoss.com/en/getting-"
"started.html#choosing-a-name."
msgstr ""
"Es poden trobar algunes indicacions més concretes a http://producingoss.com/"
"en/getting-started.html#choosing-a-name."

#. type: Block title
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:274
#, no-wrap
msgid "Register the name in important online (Internet) sites (3.3, 7.0)"
msgstr " Adquirir el nom en els espais d’Internet importants"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:283
msgid ""
"For big projects it is advisable from the outset to think about the Internet "
"sites and platforms where it is essential to have a presence and ensure the "
"domains and corresponding usernames are available.  Besides one or more own "
"Internet domains names, a project might want to be present in GitHub or "
"Twitter, for example.  Using the same username everywhere makes it easier "
"for people to identify the project, even if they are not heavily involved in "
"it."
msgstr ""
"Per projectes grans és recomanable pensar des del principi en quins llocs i "
"plataformes d’Internet s’haurà de tenir presència i assegurar la "
"disponibilitat dels dominis o noms d’usuari corresponents. A més d’un o més "
"dominis ICANN propis, pot ser que un projecte vulgui tenir presència a "
"GitHub o Twitter, per exemple. Utilitzar a tot arreu el mateix nom d’usuari "
"facilita la identificació del projecte per part de persones que encara no hi "
"estan massa involucrades."

#. type: Block title
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:286
#, no-wrap
msgid "Draw up a clear mission statement and publish it in prominent places"
msgstr ""
"Redactar una declaració de propòsit clara i posar-la a llocs destacats"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:297
msgid ""
"The mission statement is a short text of one or two paragraphs that allows "
"people to decide in 30 seconds if they are interested in carrying on reading "
"about the project or not.  It should be accompanied by the necessary links "
"in case the answer is yes.  When writing it we can assume potential readers "
"have a minimum knowledge of the project’s area of application.  People "
"without such knowledge will probably not be interested in the project."
msgstr ""
"La declaració de propòsit és un text curt, d’un o dos paràgrafs, que permet "
"a la gent decidir en 30 segons si els interessa seguir llegint sobre el "
"projecte o no. Ha d’anar acompanyada dels enllaços necessaris per si la "
"resposta afirmativa. En el redactat es pot donar per suposats uns "
"coneixements mínims de l’àrea d’aplicació del projecte. Les persones que no "
"disposen d’aquests coneixements probablement no estaran interessades en el "
"projecte."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:299
msgid ""
"The text should at least be in English and Catalan, for using the most "
"suitable version in each case."
msgstr ""
"El text s’ha de tenir redactat com a mínim en anglès i en català, per "
"utilitzar la versió que convingui en cada cas."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:301
msgid "It should appear in the following places at least:"
msgstr "Ha d’aparèixer com a mínim als següents llocs:"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:304 modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:323
msgid ""
"The home page of the website targeted at project users, if there is one.  It "
"should be capable of being seen without the need to scroll down the page on "
"a desktop computer."
msgstr ""
"La pàgina d’inici de la web orientada a usuaris del projecte, cas de tenir-"
"ne. S’ha de poder veure sense necessitat de fer scroll en un ordinador de "
"sobretaula."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:305 modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:324 modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:345 modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:372 modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:413
msgid "The `README` file of the main repository."
msgstr "El fitxer `README` del repositori principal."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:306 modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:325
msgid ""
"The project list at https://ajuntamentdebarcelona.github.io/[https://"
"ajuntamentdebarcelona.github.io]."
msgstr "El llistat de projectes a https://ajuntamentdebarcelona.github.io."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:307 modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:326
msgid ""
"Every time the project is entered in a repository or free software project "
"list, for example https://joinup.ec.europa.eu/[Join Up of the European "
"Union]."
msgstr ""
"Cada vegada que el projecte s’introdueix a un repositori o llistat de "
"projectes de codi obert, per exemple el https://joinup.ec.europa.eu/[Join Up "
"de la Unió Europea]."

#. type: Block title
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:310
#, no-wrap
msgid "Specify in prominent places that the project is free software"
msgstr "Especificar en llocs destacats que el projecte és lliure"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:320
msgid ""
"This measure is to ensure potential collaborators do not have to look too "
"far to know whether they are willing to contribute to the project or not.  "
"It is also important to state under which specific licence (including the "
"version) the software is being distributed, using the full name or "
"identifier, whichever is best in each case, exactly as they appear at https:/"
"/spdx.org/licenses/.  Specify the licence in the following places at least:"
msgstr ""
"És important, a més, indicar sota quina llicència concreta es distribueix el "
"programari (incloent la versió), utilitzant el nom complert o bé "
"l’identificador, el que més convingui en cada cas, exactament com apareixen "
"a https://spdx.org/licenses/. Especificar la llicència com a mínim en els "
"següents llocs:"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:328
msgid ""
"With regard to the website targeted at project users, it is important not to "
"relegate this to a “downloads” or “development” page which might require "
"more than one click."
msgstr ""
"En quant a la web orientada a usuaris del projecte, és important no relegar "
"aquesta informació a una pàgina de «descàrregues» o de «desenvolupament» que "
"requereixi més d’un clic."

#. type: Block title
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:331
#, no-wrap
msgid "Specify a feature list in easily accessible places"
msgstr ""
"Especificar en llocs fàcilment accessibles un llistat de funcionalitats"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:339
msgid ""
"This helps people to decide whether or not the project might cover their "
"needs."
msgstr ""
"Serveix per què la gent acabi de decidir si el projecte pot cobrir o no les "
"seves necessitats."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:341
msgid "Include the list, or create a visible link to it from at least:"
msgstr "Enllaçar de forma visible com a mínim des de:"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:344 modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:371
msgid ""
"The home page of the website targeted at project users, if there is one.  "
"The link should be capable of being seen without the need to scroll down the "
"page on a desktop computer."
msgstr ""
"*La pàgina d’inici de la web orientada a usuaris del projecte, cas de*\n"
"tenir-ne. L’enllaç s’ha de poder veure sense necessitat de fer scroll en un "
"ordinador de sobretaula."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:348
msgid ""
"This is better in the form of a list with bullet points and simple "
"sentences, or an even more graphic form.  Often it is a kind of extension of "
"the mission statement."
msgstr ""
"Millor en forma de llistat amb vinyetes i frases simples, o d’una manera "
"encara més gràfica. Molts cops és una mena d’extensió de la declaració de "
"propòsit."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:350
msgid ""
"If a feature has not been implemented yet, it can be specified in brackets "
"as: _planned_ or _work-in-progress_."
msgstr ""
"Si una funcionalitat encara no està implementada es pot especificar entre "
"parèntesis: _planned_ o _work-in-progress_."

#.  As explained in more detail in measure _M_: _Specify and maintain a website with the development status of the project_,
#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:354
msgid ""
"It makes no sense, and indeed could be counter-productive, to falsify or "
"exaggerate the product’s real technical merits."
msgstr ""
"Especificar i mantenir una pàgina amb l’estat de desenvolupament del "
"projecte, no té sentit, i de fet pot ser molt contraproduent, falsejar o "
"exagerar els veritables mèrits tècnics del producte."

#. type: Block title
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:357
#, no-wrap
msgid "Specify the main technical requirements in easily accessible places"
msgstr ""
"Especificar en llocs fàcilment accessibles els principals requeriments "
"tècnics"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:366
msgid ""
"For example, indicate what hardware/software architecture is required for "
"installing it, which operating system and so on.  This information is also "
"necessary so a potential user can see whether they can use the solution or "
"not."
msgstr ""
"Per exemple quina arquitectura hardware/software es necessita per instal·lar-"
"ho, quin sistema operatiu, etc. També és una informació necessària per què "
"un potencial usuari esbrini si pot utilitzar la solució o no."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:368
msgid ""
"Include this information, or create a visible link to it from at least:"
msgstr "Enllaçar de forma visible com a mínim des de:"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:374
msgid ""
"This is better in the form of a list with bullet points and simple sentences."
""
msgstr "Millor en forma de llistat amb vinyetes i frases simples."

#. type: Block title
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:377
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Specify the differences with similar products in easily accessible places"
msgstr ""
"Especificar en llocs fàcilment accessibles les diferències amb productes "
"similars"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:385
msgid ""
"Above all, highlight the advantages compared with better-known and well-"
"established tools, free or privately owned, but do not hide the limitations."
msgstr ""
"Destacar sobretot els avantatges respecte les eines més conegudes i ben "
"establertes, lliures o propietàries, però no amagar les limitacions."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:388
msgid ""
"Create a visible link from the website targeted at project users, if there "
"is one.  Strictly technical differences can also be linked from or included "
"on the development website."
msgstr ""
"Enllaçar de forma visible des de la web orientada a usuaris del projecte, "
"cas de tenir-ne. Les diferències estrictament tècniques també es poden "
"enllaçar des de la web de desenvolupament."

#. type: Block title
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:391
#, no-wrap
msgid "Specify and maintain a page with the development status of the project"
msgstr ""
"Especificar i mantenir una pàgina amb l’estat de desenvolupament del "
"projecte"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:399
msgid ""
"This involves writing a list which is periodically updated for each release "
"or important milestone containing:"
msgstr ""
"Es tracta d’escriure un llistat, que es va actualitzant periòdicament a cada "
"release o fita important, que contingui:"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:401
msgid ""
"The previous releases, with the publication date and the main changes that "
"were introduced."
msgstr ""
"Les release anteriors, amb la data de publicació i els principals canvis que "
"s’hi van introduir."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:402
msgid ""
"Future releases or project milestones with a tentative date as a very "
"schematic roadmap."
msgstr ""
"Futures release o fites del projecte amb data temptativa de realització, a "
"mode de full de ruta molt esquemàtic."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:404
msgid "The purpose of this page is to highlight three things:"
msgstr "L’objectiu d’aquesta pàgina és contribuir a visibilitzar tres coses:"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:406
msgid "Which milestones have been achieved."
msgstr "Quines fites s’han assolit ja."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:407
msgid ""
"Where the project is heading and how far there is to go to reach the other "
"milestones."
msgstr ""
"Cap a on es dirigeix el projecte i com de lluny es troben les fites que "
"s’espera assolir."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:408
msgid ""
"How active the project and its community are and how well maintained the "
"code is."
msgstr ""
"Com d’actius son el projecte i la seva comunitat, i com de ben mantingut "
"està el codi."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:410
msgid "Create a link from at least:"
msgstr "Enllaçar com a mínim des de:"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:412
msgid "The website targeted at project users"
msgstr "La web orientada a usuaris del projecte."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:418
msgid ""
"It is very important to be transparent and not falsify the real status of "
"the project.  It is more harmful to attract users with false expectations "
"(that it will be impossible to satisfy) than err on the side of caution when "
"outlining the progress made or expected.  All projects have defects and it "
"makes everyone's life easier (project developers, promoters and potential "
"outside users) to deal with them transparently.  Most successful free "
"software software projects have a “Known bugs” section on their website, and "
"some of these bugs stay there for years."
msgstr ""
"És molt important ser transparents i no falsejar l’estat real del projecte. "
"És més perniciós atraure usuaris amb expectatives que no es podran complir "
"que no pecar de conservadorisme a l’hora d’exposar el progrés realitzat o "
"esperat. Tots els projectes tenen defectes i facilita la vida a tothom "
"(desenvolupadors, promotors del projecte i potencials usuaris externs) "
"tractar-los amb transparència. Molts projectes de programari lliure exitosos "
"contenen a la seva pàgina un apartat titulat \"Known bugs\", i alguns "
"d’aquests defectes romanen allà durant anys."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:421
msgid ""
"What's more, in the case of free software code, the whole code and the whole "
"process can be seen by everybody, and everybody can install and test the "
"product.  Anybody can refute our affirmations if they are not certain, as "
"explained in: http://producingoss.com/en/marketing.html#goldfish-bowl."
msgstr ""
"A més, en el cas del codi obert, tot el codi i tot el procés de "
"desenvolupament està a la vista de tothom, i tothom pot instal·lar i provar "
"el producte. Qualsevol pot refutar les nostres afirmacions si no son certes, "
"com s’explica a http://producingoss.com/en/marketing.html#goldfish-bowl."

#. type: Block title
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:424
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Establish measures to improve the visibility of the progress and level of "
"activity on the project"
msgstr ""
"Establir mesures per visibilitzar millor el progrés i el grau d’activitat "
"del projecte"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:432
msgid ""
"Automatic status indicators and feedback can be placed on the home page of "
"the users’ and developers’ websites, or other places, with information from, "
"for example:"
msgstr ""
"Es poden posar indicadors i alimentadors automàtics a la pàgina d’inici de "
"les webs (tant a la d’usuaris com la de desenvolupament), o en altres llocs, "
"amb informacions que provinguin, per exemple, de:"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:434
msgid "The repository, e.g. the latest commit messages."
msgstr "El repositori, per exemple els darrers missatges de commit."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:435
msgid ""
"The continuous integration system, e.g. what builds or test series have "
"worked or failed recently."
msgstr ""
"El sistema d’integració continua, per exemple quins builds o conjunts de "
"testos han funcionat o fallat darrerament."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:436
msgid "The issue and bug notification system."
msgstr "El sistema de notificació d’incidències o defectes."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:437
msgid "Project and user Twitter profiles."
msgstr "Twitter del projecte o d’usuaris de l’aplicació."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:439
msgid ""
"Another possibility is to show in graphic form a kind of progress calendar "
"with the different versions."
msgstr ""
"També es pot mostrar de manera gràfica una mena de calendari de progrés amb "
"les diferents versions."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:441
msgid ""
"By way of example, the way the https://launchpad.net/inkscape[Ubuntu "
"Launchpad example project] information is shown could be added."
msgstr ""
"Es pot agafar com exemple la manera que mostra la informació de projectes d’ "
"https://launchpad.net/inkscape[exemple el Launchpad d’Ubuntu]."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:443
msgid ""
"The aim is to reinforce and highlight all the points made in the #h:a22a9688-"
"f8e2-473d-baf5-8989693a41c1[Measure: Specify and maintain a page with the "
"development status of the project]."
msgstr ""
"L’objectiu és enfortir i fer més visual tot allò esmentat a la #h:a22a9688-"
"f8e2-473d-baf5-8989693a41c1[Mesura: Especificar i mantenir una pàgina amb "
"l’estat de desenvolupament del projecte]."

#. type: Block title
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:446
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Negotiate beforehand how to highlight the contributions sponsored by the "
"City Council"
msgstr ""
"Negociar a priori la manera de fer visibles les aportacions patrocinades per "
"l’Ajuntament"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:455
msgid ""
"Barcelona City Council might be interested in software projects it has not "
"started but makes some sort of contribution to (add-ons, translations, hours "
"of maintenance work) recognising and publicising these contributions.  What "
"form that takes will depend on each project and the nature of the "
"contributions.  Some examples:"
msgstr ""
"A l’Ajuntament de Barcelona li pot interessar que els projectes de "
"programari que no han estat iniciats per l’Ajuntament, però als quals "
"realitza contribucions de qualsevol tipus (extensions, traduccions, hores de "
"treball de manteniment) reconeguin i donin publicitat a aquestes "
"contribucions. La manera en que això es concreti dependrà de cada projecte i "
"de la naturalesa de les aportacions. Alguns exemples poden ser:"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:457
msgid ""
"Mention in a public list of bodies that participate in or contribute to the "
"project."
msgstr ""
"Esment en una llista pública d’entitats que participen o contribueixen al "
"projecte."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:458
msgid "The City Council logo appearing in the project website."
msgstr "Aparició del logo de l’Ajuntament a la web del projecte."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:460
msgid ""
"Before initiating collaboration it is a good idea to talk with the project "
"development community about the kind of recognition the City Council would "
"like in each case."
msgstr ""
"És convenient, abans d’iniciar la col·laboració, parlar amb la comunitat de "
"desenvolupament del projecte sobre quin reconeixement desitjaria obtenir "
"l’Ajuntament en cada cas."

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:463
#, no-wrap
msgid "Parametrisation, configuration and installation"
msgstr "Parametrització, configuració i instal·lació"

#. type: Block title
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:469
#, no-wrap
msgid "Parametrise the product using configuration files"
msgstr ""
"Obligar als adjudicataris a parametritzar el producte usant fitxers de "
"configuració"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:479
msgid ""
"Do not include deployment-specific or client-specific data in the code."
msgstr ""
"No incloure al codi dades específiques d'un desplegament, o d'un client."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:482
msgid ""
"Build-time and execution-time parametrisation should be possible through "
"configuration files, even if other methods exist (e.g. command-line options)."
"  Those configuration files should be kept in a different, private "
"repository."
msgstr ""
"La parametrització, tant del procés de _build_ com de l'execució, s'ha de "
"poder realitzar a través de fitxers de configuració, fins i tot si hi ha "
"altres mètodes (per exemple, opcions de línia de línia de comandes). Aquests "
"fitxers de configuració s'han de mantenir en un repositori privat diferent."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:485
msgid ""
"This makes it easier to reuse the code.  It is incorrect to put the "
"configuration:"
msgstr ""
"Això fa més senzilla la reutilització del codi. És incorrecte posar la "
"configuració:"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:487
msgid "Hardwired in the code itself."
msgstr "Fixada estàticament al propi codi."

#.  (see the ref:measure M_A69 <measure_M_A69>).
#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:490
msgid "In files committed to the same repository as the code."
msgstr "En fitxers guardats al mateix repositori que el codi."

#. type: Block title
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:493
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Implement and document build and installation procedures with widely used "
"free tools"
msgstr ""
"Implementar i documentar procediments de build i instal·lació amb eines "
"lliures i d’ús estès"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:497
msgid "Day1"
msgstr "Dia1"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:503
msgid ""
"It is very important not to delay build and installation automation, and "
"documenting them.  Without this information, the effort any developer has to "
"put in to test the tool will probably be too great for anyone to try it."
msgstr ""
"És molt important no esperar gens a construir i documentar un sistema de "
"build del programari, ja que sense això l’esforç que ha de realitzar "
"qualsevol desenvolupador per provar l’eina serà probablement massa gran com "
"perquè ningú ho intenti."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:506
msgid ""
"Documentation has to be sufficient for third parties to understand how to "
"configure and deploy the product.  Organisations awarded with contracts have "
"to understand they will not have a monopoly over the configuration, "
"deployment and maintenance of the product."
msgstr ""
"La documentació ha de ser suficient perquè un tercer entengui com configurar "
"i desplegar el producte. Les organitzacions adjudicatàries de contractes han "
"d’entendre que no tindran el monopoli de la configuració, desplegament i "
"manteniment del producte."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:510
msgid ""
"Needless to say, users and potential collaborators in a free software "
"project cannot be forced to depend on tools that are not free as well, and, "
"it is best to choose the most commonly used ones which the majority of "
"developers are most familiar with.  That might vary from one community to "
"another.  Some examples of commonly used build tools (some of which can also "
"be used in configuration and installation procedures) that we recommend are:"
msgstr ""
"Per suposat no es pot obligar als usuaris i potencials col·laborador d’un "
"projecte de codi obert a dependre d’eines que no siguin alhora programari "
"lliure, i dins d’aquestes convé triar les d’ús més estès i que resultin més "
"familiars a la majoria de desenvolupadors. Això últim pot variar d’una "
"comunitat a una altra. Alguns exemples d’eines de build (algunes també "
"serveixen per als procediments de configuració i instal·lació) d’ús comú i "
"que recomanem son:"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:512
msgid "For Java projects: Maven, Gradle, Ant (also for other languages)."
msgstr ""
"Per a projectes Java: Maven, Ant (també serveix per altres llenguatges)."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:513
msgid ""
"For Python projects follow the advice of http://python-packaging.readthedocs."
"io/en/latest/index.html, which also includes information on packaging."
msgstr ""
"Per a projectes Python recomanem seguir els consell de http://python-"
"packaging.readthedocs.io/en/latest/index.html, que inclouen també informació "
"sobre empaquetament."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:514
msgid "For JavaScript projects (and front-end in general): Gulp."
msgstr "Per a projectes JavaScript (i per front-end en general): Gulp.js."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:515
msgid "For Ruby projects: Rake."
msgstr "Per a projectes Ruby: Rake."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:516
msgid "General use: Nix, CMake."
msgstr "Ús general: CMake, Nix."

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:519
#, no-wrap
msgid "Packaging and deployment"
msgstr "Empaquetat i desplegament"

#. type: Block title
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:525
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Get the successful bidder responsible for deployment to use the same code "
"published in the main repository"
msgstr ""
"Obligar a l’adjudicatari que fa el desplegament a usar el mateix codi "
"publicat al repositori principal"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:536
msgid ""
"As a condition of transparency, the source code used at any time in building "
"and deploying the services in production must be available in the City "
"Council’s public repository, preferably under the `master` branch.  Any "
"security patch, improvement or modification of any kind that is applied to "
"the code in production must be reflected in the repository."
msgstr ""
"Com a condició de transparència, el codi font que en cada moment s’utilitza "
"per construir (build) i desplegar els serveis en producció ha d’estar "
"disponible en el repositori públic de l’Ajuntament, preferentment sota la "
"branca master. Qualsevol patch de seguretat, millora o modificació de "
"qualsevol tipus que s’apliqui al codi en producció s’ha de reflectir al "
"repositori."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:539
msgid ""
"The code available in the public repository is the one fully covered by a "
"free software licence.  Nothing can be added to it."
msgstr ""
"El codi disponible al repositori públic és el que està cobert totalment per "
"una llicència lliure. No s’hi pot fer cap afegit."

#. type: Block title
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:542
#, no-wrap
msgid "Establish and explicit versioning policy in the ``README`` file"
msgstr "Establir una política de versions explícita en el fitxer ``README``"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:551
msgid ""
"Every repository should have an explicit versioning policy.  Software "
"projects normally use version identifiers based on `MAJOR.MINOR.PATCH` "
"number sequences."
msgstr ""
"Convé que cada repositori tingui una política de versions explícita. Els "
"projectes de programari utilitzen normalment identificadors de versions "
"basats en seqüències de nombres de l’estil `MAJOR.MINOR.PATCH`."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:555
msgid ""
"A suitable versioning policy must be chosen for each project.  Each "
"technological community (Java, Python, Drupal, etc.) might have a preferred "
"versioning policy so it is advisable to find out which one it is and stick "
"to it.  If there is no clear policy, we can subscribe to a well-known "
"generic policy, such as http://semver/[Semantic Versioning]."
msgstr ""
"Cal escollir una política de versions adient a cada projecte. Cada comunitat "
"tecnològica (Java, Python, Drupal, etcètera) pot tenir una política de "
"versions preferent i és aconsellable informar-se de quina és i adherir-s’hi. "
"En cas que no hi hagi una política clara podem adherir-nos a una política "
"genèrica i ben coneguda, com el http://semver/[Semantic Versioning]."

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:557
#, no-wrap
msgid "Use free formats and standards"
msgstr "Ús de formats i estàndards oberts"

#. type: Block title
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:563
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Check the user interface of web applications are strictly based on widely "
"adopted W3C standards"
msgstr ""
"Comprovar que la interfície d’usuari que compleix amb els estàndards del "
"W3C, en cas d’aplicacions web"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:571
msgid ""
"User interfaces, whether they are for public, administration or internal "
"use, have to comply with World Wide Web Consortium (W3C) standards.  They "
"should not require the use of features provided by privately owned browser "
"extensions."
msgstr ""
"Les interfícies web d’usuari, tant les d’ús per als ciutadans com les "
"d’administració i ús intern, han de complir amb els estàndards del World "
"Wide Web Consortium (W3C) i no han de requerir l’ús de funcionalitats "
"proporcionades per extensions propietàries dels navegadors."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:573
msgid ""
"The presentation has to be displayed correctly, and the product has to be "
"fully functional, with browsers of the following families:"
msgstr ""
"La presentació s’ha de visualitzar correctament, i el producte ha de ser "
"plenament funcional, amb els navegadors de la família:"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:575
msgid "Gecko (Firefox)"
msgstr "Gecko (Firefox)"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:576
msgid "WebKit/Blink (Chrome, Safari, Konqueror)"
msgstr "WebKit/Blink (Chrome, Safari, Konqueror)"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:577
msgid "Trident/EdgeHTML (Microsoft)"
msgstr "Trident/EdgeHTML (Microsoft)"

#. type: Block title
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:580
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Use open formats in exchanging files with the citizens and for internal use"
msgstr ""
"Utilitzar formats oberts en l’intercanvi de documents amb el ciutadà i amb "
"altres sistemes"

#.  TODO: machine-readable formats whenever useful.
#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:591
msgid ""
"Any exchange of documents that involves downloading or uploading files to "
"the developed system has to be done exclusively with open formats, as "
"defined by the Barcelona City Council xref:en/tech-sovereignty:"
"interoperability.adoc[Technological Sovereignty Guide]."
msgstr ""
"Tot l’intercanvi de documents amb el ciutadà que impliqui la descàrrega o "
"càrrega de fitxers s’ha de produir exclusivament amb formats oberts, segons "
"la definició que en dona la Guia de Compra Tecnològica de l’Ajuntament de "
"Barcelona.xref:en/tech-sovereignty:interoperability.adoc[Technological "
"Sovereignty Guide]."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:593
msgid ""
"For text documents, spreadsheets and presentations, the following formats "
"are acceptable:"
msgstr ""
"Pels documents de text, fulls de càlcul i presentacions, els següents "
"formats son acceptables:"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:595
msgid ""
"Plain Text based formats that have a stable and free implementation "
"available (for generation, edition and parsing) in all main IT platforms "
"including GNU/Linux."
msgstr ""
"Text pla basat en formats que disposen d'una implementació lliure i estable "
"(per la generació, edició i ingestió) en les principals plataformes incloent "
"GNU/Linux."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:596
msgid "OpenDocument formats, https://www.oasis-open.org/[]."
msgstr "OpenDocument Format, https://www.oasis-open.org/[]."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:597
msgid "PDF files."
msgstr "format PDF."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:599
msgid ""
"We reject proprietary formats from Microsoft Office and Apple's iWork (`."
"doc[x]`, `.ppt[x]`, etc.)"
msgstr ""
"Rebutgem formats propietaris com els de Microsoft Office i Apple iWork (`."
"doc[x]`, `.ppt[x]`, etc.)"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:601
msgid ""
"Images, audio and video will also be exchanged by means of open formats for "
"which a stable and free implementation exists in all main IT platforms "
"including GNU/Linux."
msgstr ""
"L’intercanvi d’imatges, àudio i vídeo també es realitzarà mitjançant formats "
"oberts pels quals existeixin implementacions lliures en les principals "
"plataformes informàtiques incloent GNU/Linux."

#. type: delimited block *
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:605
msgid ""
"A temporary exception to this rule is justified if we need to interchange "
"information with an existing service currently used at IMI that only accepts "
"some non-open format."
msgstr ""
"Es justifica una excepció temporal a aquesta regla si necessitem "
"intercanviar informació amb un servei actualment existent a l'IMI que només "
"accepta algun format no obert."

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:609
#, no-wrap
msgid "Internationalisation"
msgstr "Internacionalització"

#. type: Block title
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:615
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Define and budget the technical requirements so the product can be "
"translated and internationalised"
msgstr ""
"Definir i pressupostar els requeriments tècnics per què el producte pugui "
"ser traduït i internacionalitzat"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:625
msgid ""
"All the messages shown to users have to be internationalised.  Use the usual "
"mechanisms in each language/platform."
msgstr ""
"Tots els missatges mostrats a l’usuari han d’estar internacionalitzats. "
"Utilitzar els mecanismes habituals en cada llenguatge/plataforma."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:627
msgid ""
"The standard tool for multi-lingual messages in free software projects is "
"https://www.gnu.org/software/gettext/[`gettext`]."
msgstr ""
"L'eina estàndard per a missatges multi-lingües en projectes de programari "
"lliure és https://www.gnu.org/software/gettext/[`gettext`]."

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:630
#, no-wrap
msgid "Freeing software that was proprietary"
msgstr "Obertura d’un codi inicialment tancat"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:636
msgid ""
"The City Council owns the copyright of a lot of code that was not provided "
"under a free software license, and it is therefore proprietary software."
msgstr ""
"L'Ajuntament és propietari dels drets d'autor de molt codi que no es va "
"proporcionar sota una llicència de programari lliure i, per tant, és un "
"programari propietari."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:638
msgid ""
"This section addresses those issues that specifically affect the public "
"release under a free license of software components that were not delivered "
"as free software, and in most cases developed without public distribution in "
"mind."
msgstr ""
"En aquest apartat s’explica com preparar un codi que era tancat per, a "
"partir de la decisió de publicar-lo, poder-lo evolucionar i mantenir en "
"obert."

#. type: Block title
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:640
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Judge whether it is convenient or not to publicly distribute some City "
"Council software"
msgstr ""
"Jutjar la conveniència o no de publicar un codi en poder de l’Ajuntament"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:646
msgid ""
"Before releasing an existing software component or system in use at "
"Barcelona City Council under a free software licence, we need to check "
"whether:"
msgstr ""
"Abans de publicar sota llicència lliure un component o sistema software ja "
"existent i en ús a l’Ajuntament de Barcelona cal comprovar que:"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:648
msgid ""
"It corresponds to a general need: it could be useful to more institutions or "
"organisations, besides the City Council."
msgstr ""
"Correspon a una necessitat general: pot ser d’utilitat per a més "
"institucions o organitzacions, a més de l’Ajuntament."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:649
msgid ""
"It has some aspect that sets it apart from other, existing free software "
"solutions."
msgstr ""
"Té algun aspecte que el diferencia favorablement d’altres solucions obertes "
"existents."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:650
msgid ""
"Barcelona City Council holds legal title over the whole code it aims to "
"release, or can obtain legal title."
msgstr ""
"L’Ajuntament de Barcelona és titular legal de tot el codi que es pretén "
"alliberar, o pot fer gestions per obtenir aquesta titularitat."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:651
msgid "It can be used on free software platforms."
msgstr "Es pot executar sobre plataformes lliures."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:652
msgid ""
"The code (and associated documentation) is sufficiently developed and of a "
"high enough quality, or the improvement requirements have been clearly "
"identified and there is a strategy for tackling them."
msgstr ""
"El codi (i la documentació associada) té la qualitat i la maduresa "
"suficients, o bé els requeriments de millora estan clarament identificats i "
"existeix una estratègia per abordar-los."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:653
msgid "Freeing the code will not pose any legal risks for either party."
msgstr "L’obertura de la solució no suposarà riscos legals per a cap part."

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:654
msgid ""
"Resources are available for responding to maintenance issues until this "
"responsibility is handed over to other bodies or organisations, possibly a "
"free software community of developers and users."
msgstr ""
"Es disposa dels recursos per respondre a incidències de manteniment mentre "
"no es traspassi aquesta responsabilitat a d’altres entitats, possiblement "
"una comunitat oberta de desenvolupadors i usuaris."

#. type: Block title
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:657
#, no-wrap
msgid "Look for sensitive information or user settings in the code repository"
msgstr ""
"Buscar al repositori de codi informació sensible o configuracions d’usuari"

#. type: Block title
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:664
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Notify in new public spaces geared towards developers that this was a non-"
"free project"
msgstr ""
"Avisar als nous espais públics orientats a desenvolupadors que aquest era un "
"projecte tancat"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/ROOT/pages/collaborative-development.adoc:673
msgid ""
"This means explaining that, up to a certain date, the project did not "
"operate in the public eye, so some inconvenience is to be expected.  "
"Developer and user expectations regarding the quality and transparency of "
"some aspects of the project need to be lowered.  The commitments made to "
"make it possible to free the code also need explaining.  For example, there "
"may be lots of sensitive data in the code repository (specific user data, "
"etcetera) so it has been decided to remove the version control history and "
"create a new top-skim repository that only contains the latest version."
msgstr ""
"Es tracta d’explicar que el projecte ha funcionat fins a un determinat "
"moment com un projecte tancat i per tant cal esperar certes inconveniències. "
"Convé reduir les expectatives del nous usuaris i desenvolupadors en quant a "
